data.name: label7.Text
data.value:
GroupView control can be customized using various appearance and behavior attributes, to create a wide range of interfaces such as lists with large / small images, regular / flow view, button type selection, flat look and selective item highlighting / underlining.
The below provided options shows the possibilities of GroupView to clone Microsoft OutlookBar, Microsoft VS.NET toolbox window, Office 2000 and Office XP FolderBrowser, MSN Messenger SideBar list and XPTaskBar List.
